{
  "title": "Crunchy Creamy Dutch Chicken Stir-fry",
  "description": "This savory and creamy one-pot dutch dish features mayonnaise in a high-protein-friendly meal that slow-cooks for tender flavors.",
  "cuisine": "Chinese",
  "diet": [
    "high-protein-friendly"
